body_html: @rmlarsen So what am I supposed to do? The whole_file_reader_op is used by label_image. It was added to make label_image work on Android. Surely you can remove whole_file_reader_op and I think label_image will still build without problem. Just label_image won't be able to find the whole_file_reader_op at run-time on Android.
